sentences:
Sentence 0:
For these reasons, the effects of atrazine (5 and 50 microg/L) on several endpoints related to reproductive fitness were examined in fathead minnows (Pimephales promelas) in a 21-d static exposure.

Sentence 1:
Estradiol (0.5 microg/L) was included as a positive-control treatment.
sentence_raw: For these reasons, the effects of atrazine (5 and 50 microg/L) on several endpoints related to reproductive fitness were examined in fathead minnows (Pimephales promelas) in a 21-d static exposure.
Estradiol (0.5 microg/L) was included as a positive-control treatment.
